/* ========================================================================== */

/*   This stylesheet is laid out as follows:           

      1. Import Fonts     
      
      2. Classes used in all pages - these are prefixed with "gen-"   

      3. Classes used in index.html only - these are prefixed with "ind-"  

      4. Classes used in tours.html only - these are prefixed with "tour-"  

      5. Classes used in music.html only - these are prefixed with "mus-"  

      6. Classes used in gallery.html only - these are prefixed with "gall-"  

      7. Classes used in contact.html only - these are prefixed with "con-" 
      
      8. Bootstrap classes that I have modified
      
      NOTE: Where a class is modified by a Media Query, I have added the 
      Media Query after the relevant class so that they're easy to see.   
      
      Colors arrived at using color picker website (https://www.w3schools.com/colors/colors_picker.asp)
      and color wheel (https://www.sessions.edu/color-calculator/), and colors used in code institute course - e.g. #fafafa. */

/* ============================================================================*/

